data.description: Welcome Home! Nestled within DeLand’s highly sought after community of Victoria Park is this beautiful 3 bedroom, 3 bath, open concept home originally built by David Weekly Homes. As you enter, you are greeted by gorgeous solid wood and ceramic tile flooring throughout the large living area that is perfect for large gatherings. You will love the spacious kitchen that is full of custom features. This home also features over $50,000 worth of custom upgrades including custom office cabinets, plantation shutters throughout, crown molding, pull out cabinet shelving and more! As you walk outside, you'll notice the large screened in lanai that is perfect for entertaining while you enjoy the lush landscaping. Don’t forget the oversized garage that includes a workshop with cabinets. Amenities available within the community include 2 pools, 2 workout facilities, a tennis court, golf course, and a restaurant! Conveniently located near shopping, restaurants, major roadways, trails and much more! New HVAC installed December 2019. Call to schedule your private showing today before this one is gone. Thank you!
